# ===============================================
# API SETUP INSTRUCTIONS
# ===============================================

# GENIUS API SETUP:
# 1. Go to https://genius.com/api-clients
# 2. Create a new API client
# 3. Copy the "Client Access Token" (not Client ID/Secret)
# 4. Set GENIUS_API_KEY=your_access_token

# MUSIXMATCH API SETUP:
# 1. Go to https://developer.musixmatch.com/
# 2. Sign up for a developer account
# 3. Create a new application
# 4. Copy the API key from your app dashboard
# 5. Set MUSIXMATCH_API_KEY=your_api_key

# ===============================================
# NOTES AND DOCUMENTATION
# ===============================================

# Enhanced API Rate Limits (for reference):
# - Genius: 100 requests per minute, 1,000 per hour
# - Musixmatch: 20 requests per minute, 1,000 per hour
# - LyricFind: Enterprise rate limits (contact provider)
# - Discogs: 60 requests per minute, 1 per second

# Enhanced Features:
# - Comprehensive track credits (composers, producers, engineers)
# - Full lyrics with copyright information
# - Technical audio analysis (key, tempo, energy, etc.)
# - Publishing rights and splits breakdown
# - Recording location and production details
# - Platform availability and IDs across services

# Security Notes:
# - Always use HTTPS in production
# - Keep API keys secure and rotate regularly
# - Use strong SECRET_KEY (32+ characters)
# - Enable CORS only for trusted domains
# - Monitor API usage to avoid rate limiting

# Performance Notes:
# - Enhanced analysis may take 10-30 seconds per track
# - Consider implementing background processing for bulk operations
# - Cache enhanced results to avoid repeated API calls
# - Monitor quota usage for lyrics APIs

# Deployment Notes:
# - Set PRODUCTION=true for production deployments
# - Configure proper logging and monitoring
# - Use environment-specific settings
# - Enable automated backups
# - Set up health checks for uptime monitoring